Sam,<br><br>
Thanks for sharing your feelings and experience. It is a powerful message to this country and the world.<br><br>
It took me 27 years to begin to wake up and start the rocky and painful road &quot;home&quot;. I am still on that road, and probably will be always.<br><br>
